{"id":"02b20522-8428-4ede-a1e2-704696d04fff","title":"1522/08/02: footnote 5","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"0f6b6068-ba45-48e5-9bcb-4d60ba92209c","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"I think that the following document, dated 8th February, 1516, ","standoffProperties":[{"id":"68d98eb9-684c-4942-a8dd-72f8fbd3a641","type":"codex/time-reference","start":43,"end":60,"value":"ffac045f-af00-4006-84db-e0402afca871","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0c6b7aee-8c97-415d-bc92-8fc963eee5c9","type":"style/superscript","start":44,"end":45,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"bd58f3a8-5fda-472d-8cfe-b5e9f49e45ac","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"respecting the canonisation of this illustrious Florentine, may be ","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"7e03b8c1-7bab-43ce-a986-03525fa5e4a6","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"of interest: \u0022The Magnificent and exalted Signori, the Sisnori Priori ","standoffProperties":[{"id":"b54e5743-765d-4805-a5ac-674cc763bcd8","type":"language","start":42,"end":48,"value":"it","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"76de571b-2cc5-4340-b693-a99e6cb19196","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"di Liberta, and the gonfaloniere di giustizia, of the Florentine ","standoffProperties":[{"id":"927d1991-f885-470f-8c29-0c9fcdaecf14","type":"style/italics","start":20,"end":44,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"fd673c96-84b4-4196-a0f9-259b5dcb22fd","type":"language","start":20,"end":44,"value":"it","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"d8d1d4f5-0732-4118-bb02-a470c8cc2eb0","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":20,"end":44,"value":"c9c08553-c914-4ba7-8647-b1e6f8d6a212","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"333e820c-f0c1-4ae2-85ce-fe272d6302e8","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"People, malce known and manifest to all and any of whatsoever ","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"8ece4ce0-03e7-417a-b1d7-ef44ccbd76f9","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"rank, quality or condition they may be, that His Holiness our ","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"d8cb1cb7-ae3a-4a31-9f22-b6b2c9a89550","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Signore Pope Leone, moved by the odour of the good life and repute, ","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"849f0dae-d45b-4268-b3e5-5bd554278f65","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"and by the miracles worked through the merits of the Beato Antonino, ","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"f4458a75-6a37-42b8-b100-4c926503004f","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"formerly Archbishop of Florence, and desiring for the aforesaid ","standoffProperties":[{"id":"f99a1ed1-bfc6-4fb4-9c72-0366b7f77a81","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":23,"end":30,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"9d9d8c9d-0b43-46fc-b430-097ee61cbcae","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"reasons to canonise him, have commissioned for the execution of ","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"9b39e5b2-a251-45ec-9f67-4b2cf94b8c1a","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"this matter the Most Reverend Fathers Jacopo Simonecta and ","standoffProperties":[{"id":"a3f436d2-fc11-4615-86c7-859946fef923","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":38,"end":53,"value":"2a10c77e-38a2-471c-ac97-dfa1264ed47f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"1d93cf3c-2c76-4c01-aced-91610b5951e8","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Guglielmo Cassadoro, Auditors of the Ruota, to receive information ","standoffProperties":[{"id":"7cb658f1-716c-4e49-87a1-a023763bd20c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":18,"value":"af9cb862-d039-4dc3-ada8-68ef3185e1dc","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"4eaae899-1427-4bf2-9df9-57a15ee32912","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"respecting the said matters, from each and every person; therefore ","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"b2308918-9c6e-4e2f-99a9-e4d6033ede4b","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"the said Auditors are prepared, like obedient servants, benignly to","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"1a2646d4-8a54-4a07-8b4f-e95675714522","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"receive all information, and to examine everything, as is usual, ","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"b2915687-6e96-4ba1-88aa-9a6686727d2c","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"necessary and opportune in such matters; and it is notified to every ","standoffProperties":[{"id":"5604497c-3a4c-4d72-b8e3-66787b9c3d14","type":"hyphen","start":68,"end":68,"value":null,"zeroPoint":true,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"ad0c67a5-6066-4b51-9dc7-d0d477718fbc","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"one that they are so sent. Furthermore, the Magnificent Signori ","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"11862a1c-e7be-4fea-8286-02b56b92061c","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"and Gonfaloniere. notify to each and all, who may know anything ","standoffProperties":[{"id":"60c2b892-c5be-4032-91cf-486a1ed4d1d4","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":4,"end":15,"value":"87210999-7973-4ee1-b570-398af242075c","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"f036b855-34b9-4642-a6f5-c3a5bcdd358e","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"of the life, repute and miracles of the Beato Antonino, either per ","standoffProperties":[{"id":"f2e6af4c-ba52-4bbe-b131-1c33707ed235","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":40,"end":53,"value":"f4cc8f3e-9bb1-49a4-a071-2f623538f7bf","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"1190c62d-85eb-4101-a43d-3371fe1ecfb8","type":"hyphen","start":66,"end":66,"value":null,"zeroPoint":true,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"f4a65634-f2e6-46b2-86b0-e87509c1440d","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"sonally or by hearsay, for the love, honour and glory of God and the ","standoffProperties":[{"id":"698762c4-af28-4581-b0f8-bd1ed09581fc","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":57,"end":59,"value":"a3fed3ec-1814-4027-a2d5-ac598b2fcb6f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"c7e21653-79ac-43d4-adf7-1694ddd2c456","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Saints, to be pleased to advise and notify the said Auditors of such ","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"7c15f412-224b-409d-81b1-3c00c2f8c846","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"facts, in the house of the aforesaid M. Jacopo Simonecta, situated ","standoffProperties":[{"id":"3139834c-ed45-45e1-89b0-523e1b6c51fc","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":37,"end":55,"value":"2a10c77e-38a2-471c-ac97-dfa1264ed47f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"a3fd066e-84f0-4238-aa0f-8974d66a0fe8","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in the Via de\u0027 Pandolfini in Florence, where they will be benignantly ","standoffProperties":[{"id":"508e1217-2f10-4f99-8593-b944c9a4db3b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":7,"end":24,"value":"e34bcd6e-6582-4b8d-a546-278d58b6f211","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"8be88100-7934-40a0-a13b-8568b84fbda4","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":29,"end":36,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"7e25aded-e98e-4860-b622-8c684cf7b6a2","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"received and granted audience at any hour of the day\u0022 (Registro di ","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"b744c43e-f5f1-4ab9-aa3a-0712273defe9","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Deliberazioni de\u0027 Signori e Collegi, ad an.).","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]}]}